    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Also, at 3rd level, you have learned to guarantee a fatal blow by hitting a creature in a specific point.</p><p> When you make a melee attack, you may spend 3 cursed energy to attempt to critically injure a target.</p><p> You may roll your 3:7 dice.</p><p> On a result of a 3 or 7, you increase the damage dealt as if you activated Black Flash.</p><p> If this was activated alongside the Black Flash, treat the target as if they had the Cursed condition.</p><p></p>",
